channel.title: How to change port on server?
channel.description: heyy i recently just found a free webclient making site its pretty awsome. it says to list the port but it only says 43594 and 5555 but my source runs on a 43676 can i somehow change this port to make the webclient??

item.title: How to change port on server?
item.dc:creator: @Scape-JAVA Scape-JAVA
item.description:
@Scape-JAVA wrote:

Typically in server class (server.java), look for something like

public static int serverlistener Port = 43594; //43594 default port
If you find something similar to that, change it to your desired port.
